properties.Name: InsurancePolicyBreachBehavior
properties.Description: The one or more Breach Behaviors reported for the associated Customer Account.

Columns.Name: BreachBehaviorId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a specific breach behavior act being recorded.

Columns.Name: BreachBehaviorDate
Columns.Description: The date of the breach or on which the Breach Behavior was performed.

Columns.Name: BreachBehaviorTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Breach Behavior.

Columns.Name: BreachBehaviorDescription
Columns.Description: A description of the Breach Behavior.

Columns.Name: BreachFollowupActionDescription
Columns.Description: A description of the followup action that was performed or the action taken by the company.

Columns.Name: BreachFollowupActionTimestamp
Columns.Description: The timestamp that the followup action was performed.

Columns.Name: BreachBehaviorNote
Columns.Description: Notes, comments or additional information regarding the resolution of the Breach Behavior.

Columns.Name: InsurancePolicyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Insurance Policy.
